<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>&lt;!-- Checkbox placed --&gt;
&lt;input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="maker_check" value="1"onchange="valueChanged()"&gt;
&lt;label class="form-check-label" for="defaultCheck1"&gt;

&lt;!-- Show/Hide Box --&gt;
&lt;div id="_maker"&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Hello World!&lt;/p&gt;  
&lt;/div&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>JS:</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>function valueChanged()
{
  if($('#maker_check').is(":checked"))
  $("#_maker").show();
  else
  $("#_maker").hide();
}
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>jQuery:</p>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>// jQuery is needed 
